settings.description: watch out above! due to screencrunch of the GBA, you might wanna be extra careful in jumping high in this piranha infested cavern of pipes!

who would've thought that such a strange combo would come to be! best to learn how to use them though, and swim swiftly about with such!
PS: I am bad at underwater levels.
Hurry up, and reach the goal before time runs out!
watch out! while there may be some nice treasure at the end, you'll need to use some lavaproof beachballs to cross through this dangerous pipeline!
cannons, cannons, and more cannons are all about what this airship is! think you can deal with Larry and his tricks in the end?
Galoombas! Galoombas as far as the eye can see! where do they all come from, nobody knows!
Bullets everywhere, and they're all dangerous! either they'll turn back to try to hit you again, or just seek you down for the perfect shot!

no scenery in the main area sadly.
either way, think you can brave this giant fortress and stop Boom Boom? for this time he's got some help!
so many fire bros! well, it's not too many, but still! watch your step in this heated nighttime desert level!
Traverse Bowser's airships to find and defeat him!
vcs tem que me ajudar escapar daqui na prissao, me ajuda!!!!!!!
